      ** Return Code
     C                   PARM                    RetCodeIn
 
      ** Other parms
 
      ** Field(s) requiring validation
      ** Broker Indicator,
     C                   PARM                    DDBKIN
 
      ** OUTPUTS
 
      ** Error fields/message IDs/message data (arrays) from/to caller
     C                   PARM                    FldNamXAr
     C                   PARM                    MsgIDXAr
     C                   PARM                    MsgDtaXAr
      ** Broker Indicator - OK
     C                   PARM                    DDBKINOK
 
